Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想大哭一场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时也不是孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的梦想在闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它找回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把双眼闭上便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中的一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算留下伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕 现在是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃 Step by Step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓着梦想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常也和你一起向明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进 Step by Step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想坚信着 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想向着天空大声呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧着 in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配了在遥远天空上的星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以第七星界为目标展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在身处的是有趣热带的第四星界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪着黑球来到复活岛石像的城堡的我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了魔界三兄弟所乘的黑龙角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸被封进了暗黑空间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二十八话\N超激斗!龙星丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火子,喂,火子不要一直睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来,火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈…终于动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了,黑球呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,那个黑黑的球被那巨大的魔神拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,失去了龙神丸的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是个普通没有力量的小鬼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼,你已经不是什么救世主了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吸进了暗黑空间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸便不会再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星界山拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把星界山…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会放弃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会放弃的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去把龙神丸带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会连你也不能回来的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节巴利、雪京芭!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关闭暗黑空间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把渡他们永远封闭在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以给你这样做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在渡回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会给你把出口关闭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前我们做你对手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,死不足惜的家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧,去死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们暂时便在这里躺一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一会会好好了结你们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即把暗黑空间关闭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生,把黑球还给我!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油,火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混…混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里便是暗黑空间?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样去哪里找才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救命!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,不要过来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺负女孩子,不可饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最怕蜘蛛的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,真是行衰运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫渡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是暗黑空间的精灵艾玛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这种地方干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来找一部叫龙神丸的魔神的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有见过?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是刚才丢进来的魔神吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里见到的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,为了报答你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要到龙神丸那里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过这个沼泽是捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这里不知道会有什么东西袭击的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有勇气过去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像隐约有点不祥感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?刚才不是还说有勇气过去的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,虽然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?怎么突然觉得很想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了会发生很可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?可怕的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这样说也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明已叫他不可以睡的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说过会发生很可怕的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷失了在这个世界的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以让他们有命回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何会这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…死了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢,死了便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾玛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,艾玛小姐也没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是死亡野原啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一踏进这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便只能看着前面走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一回头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体便会变成石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变石头!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你也要去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了把龙神丸带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定会死的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,你来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回头看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的剑和我的鱼叉交换的约定怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡和我们玩赛跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里谁也没有来!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸他在求救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,你在哪里!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快救我,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体好像被火烧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不来救我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所认识的龙神丸是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸是绝不会说示弱的话的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已穿过死亡野原了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回头看也没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才险些变成石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等,龙神丸啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听不见我的声音吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸被黑暗石像夺去了意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗石像?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是支配着这个暗黑空间的可怕石像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是黑暗石像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入了暗黑空间的魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都会被那石像握碎掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么龙神丸也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,不可以去那边的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了打倒那石像外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他方法救龙神丸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那石像?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎样做?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:12:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石像的额头上有颗宝石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它打破便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去试试!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾玛小姐在这里等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真是看不下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等我,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾玛小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石像变成了岩石了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,今天真的是行大衰运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾玛小姐,你没有事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了,龙神丸呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧,艾玛小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点,龙神丸…龙神丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙…龙神丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?这把剑是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有真正的救世主才能得到的光之剑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会知道这些事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你复活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡重夺回来的这光明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给了我力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多谢你,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,不是我一个人的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这里的艾玛小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾…艾玛小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来黑暗石像便是为了封印光龙剑而建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多坏达还把这光明空间变成了暗黑空间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被改变姿态失去了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过,全靠渡的活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令这世界和我也恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真名叫芙丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是守护光龙剑的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,这把剑便应该要还给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把剑已经是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在外面封闭这空间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你赶快出发吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,那再见了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的力量已变得能把黑暗变为光明了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那力量一定会令龙神丸得到新的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要输给这样的风!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,拔剑吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔剑?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟被喽啰们坏了我的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的力量已变得能把黑暗变为光明了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一种力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我得到了新的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你叫现在的我做龙星丸吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡第一名,渡超了不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔界三兄弟!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次到救世主渡做你们对手!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,这样的话再来多一次魔界力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送你去回不了来的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超炎龙拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光龙剑吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个仇我一定会报的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我记着啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅、古拿玛、火美子!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下相信你一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且,龙神丸的力量也好像增强了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是会靠师傅和古拿玛在牵制着黑龙角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不向那家伙道谢也不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那部魔神是海火子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已没有多坏达的手下在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,救世主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你把海水恢复原状吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着到第五星界了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?这个胸口在驱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop! 已不能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也一个劲儿地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油门不用放开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直踏着 Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:23:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是速度的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TONIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直望着的瞳孔涌上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.53,0:23:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜 MY LOVE

